name: Super Jank 5-Hole Golf Roll
description:
CONTROLS

  • WASD to Move
  • 1/2/3/4 to switch between Camera Angles
  • Q to reset current hole

Roll your way around 5 small, separate courses in this short little "golf" game. Unfortunately I didn't have as much time as I wanted to work on this thanks to some other game jams and general life activities getting in the way, so RIP actual golfing physics and a full 9 hole course than I had dreamed of when I started working. But hey, something is better than nothing right?

64x64 resolution, scaled up to 640 x 640 for the web player.

A weird, not so great "golf" game made for the LowRezJam 2019! Created with Kenny Assets
